---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>关于我</title>
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: "Segoe UI", "PingFang SC", "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;
        background: #0f172a;
        color: #f8fafc;
      }

      .wrap {
        width: min(800px, calc(100% - 32px));
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 40px 0 80px;
      }

      a {
        color: #93c5fd;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .card {
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        border-radius: 20px;
        padding: 28px;
        line-height: 1.9;
      }

      h1 {
        margin-top: 0;
      }

      p {
        color: #cbd5e1;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="wrap">
      <p><a href={base}>← 返回首页</a></p>

      <section class="card">
        <h1>关于我</h1>
        <p>你好，我是载酒寻歌。</p>
        <p>CTF小白 | 持之以恒的学习者</p>
        <p>这里会写：</p>
        <p>1. 我的生活碎片<br />2. 我的成长日记<br />3. 一些阿巴阿巴</p>
        <p>Welcome to my world</p>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>